# Philips Hue Bridge Hue LED Smart Lights
## Product Description
The Philips Hue Bridge Hue LED Smart Lights are compatible with Amazon Alexa, Apple HomeKit, and The Google Assistant. This product includes 1 Hue Bridge, which is the heart of the Philips Hue system. It allows users to start building or expanding their ecosystem and control their lights from wherever they are.

## Key Features
* Compatible with Amazon Alexa, Apple HomeKit, and The Google Assistant
* Includes 1 Hue Bridge
* Control up to 50 Philips Hue lights with a single bridge
* Wireless and smart control features

## Product Specifications
* Finish Type: White
* Bulb Base: B22D
* Item Weight: 200 Grams
* Switch Type: Touch
* Style: Hue Bridge Gen 2.0
* Brand: Philips Hue
* Colour: White
* Special Feature: Smart Control, Wireless, Smart Light
* Light Source Type: LED
* Material: Synthetic

